  "raw_content": "12SPC UMA4 MMA性能评估\n1.需求描述\n在12spc的机器上，实现UMA4的MMA，用于评估算子性能\n测试模型\nllama1-7b：{ 4096， 4096}，{11008，4096}\n2.实现方案\n需要进行的改动：\nHost侧\n权重tensor的构造需要改为UMA4，左矩阵继续保持UMA\n拆分到每个SPC上之后的权重，即W_block，需要进行32对齐\nKernel侧\nldgmb：针对于每个SPC，比如0-2，每次访问到的region均是0号，即起始地址是0，那么SPC0访问到的就是0，SPC1访问到的也是0，但是实际它需要去处理的是 blockIdx.x * W_block = 352，SPC2需要去访问的是 blockIdx.x * W_block = 352 * 2。\n但是对于第二个region，这个起始地址是传进来，然后在里面计算\ntypecast：输出访问是UMA16\n3.性能测试（时间单位为ms）\ntest_case \nTEST(MmaFunc, test_12spc) {\n    float mesc = 0.0;\n    // constexpr int32_t SPC_NUM = 12;\n    EXPECT_TRUE((test_MatMul_FoldW<S8, SPC_NUM, SPC_NUM, SPC_NUM, CASE4_TYPECAST_S8>(32, 4096, 4096, mesc, 10)));\n\n    EXPECT_TRUE((test_MatMul_FoldW<S8, SPC_NUM, SPC_NUM, SPC_NUM, CASE4_TYPECAST_S8>(32, 4096, 4096, mesc, 10)));\n    EXPECT_TRUE((test_MatMul_FoldW<S8, SPC_NUM, SPC_NUM, SPC_NUM, CASE4_TYPECAST_S8>(32 * 512, 4096, 4096, mesc, 10)));\n    EXPECT_TRUE((test_MatMul_FoldW<S8, SPC_NUM, SPC_NUM, SPC_NUM, CASE4_TYPECAST_S8>(32, 11008, 4096, mesc, 10)));\n    EXPECT_TRUE((test_MatMul_FoldW<S8, SPC_NUM, SPC_NUM, SPC_NUM, CASE4_TYPECAST_S8>(32 * 512, 11008, 4096, mesc, 10)));\n}\n\n\n\n右矩阵类型\n\n\n\nNxS\n\nNUMA (ms)\n\nUMA4 (ms)\n\n\n\nNUMA\n\nUMA4\n\n16SPC\n\n(4096, 4096)\n\n32 x 1\n\n0.0628\n\n0.0703\n\n共50个结果，前10个为warm-up case，后面每10个一组对应左边的shape\n\n\nreport-1215436.txt\n\n\n\n\nreport-1217012.txt\n\n\n\n\n\n32 x 512\n\n2.8975\n\n2.9139\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n(11008, 4096)\n\n32 x 1\n\n0.1144\n\n0.1393\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n32 x 512\n\n7.4360\n\n7.416\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n12SPC\n(16spc mask为12spc)\n命令为：0x7777\n\n(4096, 4096)\n\n32 x 1\n\n0.064\n\n0.0684\n\n\n\n\nreport-1220456.txt\n\n\n\n\n\n\nreport-1219579.txt\n\n\n\n\n\n32 x 512\n\n2.9859\n\n2.9978\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n(11008, 4096)\n\n32 x 1\n\n0.1219\n\n0.1307\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n32 x 512\n\n8.2831\n\n8.128\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nLLama2-7B:\n\n\n\n\n\n\nweight\n\n16spc numa\n\n15spc numa(0x7fff)\n\n14spc numa (0x77ff)\n\n12spc numa(0x7777)\n\n12